<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <title>Tribute to Ada Lovelace</title>
</head>
<body>
    <main id="main">
        <h1 id="title">Ada Lovelace</h1>
        <p>The Enchantress of Numbers</p>

        <div id="img-div">
            <img id="image" src="ada_lovelace.jpg" alt="Portrait of Ada Lovelace">
            <div id="img-caption">Ada Lovelace, the visionary who recognized the potential of the Analytical Engine.</div>
        </div>

        <section id="tribute-info">
            <h3>Life and Legacy</h3>
            <p>Ada Lovelace was a mathematician and writer, chiefly known for her work on Charles Babbage's early mechanical general-purpose computer, the Analytical Engine.</p>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <a id="tribute-link" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ada_Lovelace" target="_blank">
                Read more about Ada Lovelace on Wikipedia
            </a>
        </footer>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
